title: G-SHOCK X COMPLEX Greg Mike featuring GDX6900CM Watch
description:
There is no concealing the style appeal of a G-SHOCK - even when it's camouflaged. The timepiece leader's new multi-angle print camo line brings the classic military look - and modern streetwear staple - to the wrists of intrepid adventurers the world over. But this camouflage's effect is actually counterintuitive; rather than causing the watch blend in, it makes it stand out from the rest.

To celebrate the launch, G-SHOCK has selected Atlanta-based artist Greg Mike to create an installation at the GSHOCK Soho store in New York City. The partnership is a natural fit. Mike has been exposed to the power of reinventing public spaces through art from an early age, when he took frequent excursions to 1980s-era New York City. As an artist, he's honed a style that's both playful and subversive, drawing inspiration from a range of popular mediums including graffiti, street art and comics. Like G-SHOCK, he now stands at the forefront of his field, and never blends in.
